   <li>
    <p>&lsquo;<a href="#text-space-collapse"><code class=property>text-space-collapse</code></a>&rsquo;  &lsquo;<code class=css>preserve</code>&rsquo; ˒ߒ꒤쒤ƒ뒾쒹璡גǒΒǒʬ䒤쒤ʒڒ non-breaking spaces(Β֒쒡ڒ)Ȓƒ쒤뒡ԒϒڒΒ꒤˒¸ߒ뒡

