   <pre><code>&lt;ltr&gt;A<span class=egbidiwsaA>&#160;</span>&lt;rtl&gt;<span class=egbidiwsbB>&#160;</span>B<span class=egbidiwsaB>&#160;</span>&lt;/rtl&gt;<span class=egbidiwsbC>&#160;</span>C&lt;/ltr&gt;</code></pre>

   <p>ג <code>&lt;ltr&gt;</code> ϒ钱˒ʒԒ뒤Ȓɽג <code>&lt;rtl&gt;</code> ϒ钺ؒʒԒ뒤Ȓɽ &lsquo;<a href="#text-space-collapse"><code class=property>text-space-collapse</code></a>&rsquo; ג풥ђƒ &lsquo;<code class=css>collapse</code>&rsquo; ˒ߒ꒤쒤ƒ뒾쒹璡ҒΒΒ뒲̒ʒΒ蒤˒ʒ:</p>

